{"tid":2242781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"到駐港台北經濟文化辦　管浩鳴不回應是否與陳同佳有關","createTime":"2020-10-14T09:07:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T09:07:21.000Z","uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"89afca273aa3c7fae8b63d70f1c96b8963e466a6","tid":2242781,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T09:07:21.000Z","msg":"有傳媒報道，一直協助台灣殺人案疑犯陳同佳的聖公會教省秘書長管浩鳴，下午到位於金鐘力寶中心的台北經濟文化辦事處，並拍攝到他手持文件和護照。<br />\n<br />\n管浩鳴回應查詢時表示，到台北經濟文化辦事處是辦理私人事情，詳情不便透露。<br />\n<br />\n被問到與陳同佳赴台有沒有任何關係，管浩鳴說，暫時不想回應，有進一步消息再通知。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1554719-20201014.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1554719-20201014.htm&d=Tp8cMPEgSVVC2rtXaxUH2kYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=60739ecc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1554719-20201014.htm&h=4966b6c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1554719-20201014.htm</a>"}]}